        <div class="col-lg-9">
            <div class="bg-light p-4 p-lg-5 rounded-3">
                <section id="introduction" class="mb-5">
                    <div class="border-start border-4 border-primary ps-3 mb-4">
                        <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Introduction</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>At LearnConnect, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we look after your personal data when you visit our website and tell you about your privacy rights and how the law protects you.</p>
                    <p>Please read this privacy policy carefully before using our services.</p>
                </section>

                <section id="information-collect" class="mb-5">
                    <div class="border-start border-4 border-primary ps-3 mb-4">
                        <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">Information We Collect</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>We collect several types of information from and about users of our website, including:</p>
                    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4 mb-3">
